SUMMARY:Hands Off Our Education Rally - by Canadian Federation of
  Students-Ontario
LOCATION:Queen’s Park
DESCRIPTION:More info: https://www.instagram.com/p/DVhAh4BETBS/\n\nHosted
  by Canadian Federation of Students-Ontario
  (https://cfsontario.ca/)\n\nStudents won’t be silenced or pushed
  around. They’re just getting started - and we won’t stop until this
  government puts people over profit. Let’s welcome Doug Ford’s
  Government back from their extended vacation with a bang! Join CSFON
  along with OPSEU and CUPE to demand an end to the privatization and cuts
  to public education and services.
END:VEVENT
