SUMMARY:Volunteer for Renters’ Rights - by Progress Toronto
LOCATION:St George Station
DESCRIPTION:More info:
  https://www.progresstoronto.ca/vol-mar-24-2026\n\nHosted by Progress
  Toronto
  (https://www.toronto.ca/services-payments/streets-parking-transportation/
 transportation-projects/rapidto/rapidto-bathurst-street/)\n\nDoug Ford’s
  government passed new legislation (Bill 60) that makes it easier for
  landlords to evict renters and make finding an affordable place to live
  even harder. Join Progress Toronto in knocking on doors inside rental
  buildings across Toronto to make sure Ford still feels the pressure for
  his threats to renters.
END:VEVENT
