SUMMARY:The Future of E-Bikes: Community Bikeways + Fix - by Toronto
  Community Bikeways Coalition
LOCATION:Fix Coffee + Bikes
DESCRIPTION:More info:
  https://www.eventbrite.ca/e/the-future-of-e-bikes-community-bikeways-fix-
 tickets-1985008763647\n\nHosted by Toronto Community Bikeways Coalition
  (https://www.communitybikewaysto.ca/)\n\nE-Bikes are transforming urban
  transportation\, offering a clean\, affordable and efficient mode of
  travel\, but any new technology comes with growing pains. Come for an
  evening of discussions on bike design\, the existing regulatory regime
  and the future of e-bike regulation.
END:VEVENT
