SUMMARY:The Walrus Talks Opioids - by The Walrus
LOCATION:Isabel Bader
DESCRIPTION:More info:
  https://www.eventbrite.ca/e/the-walrus-talks-opioids-tickets-198220703760
 9\n\nHosted by The Walrus (https://thewalrus.ca/)\n\nIt’s been nearly a
  decade since the Ontario government released its official opioid
  strategy\, but recent findings from the Office of the Auditor General and
  the Office of the Chief Coroner show the crisis continues to deepen. Come
  hear from experts and explore how policy\, care\, and community can
  transform lives amidst a drug toxicity crisis.
END:VEVENT
