SUMMARY:Civic Meetup - Headway Management Using Real-Time Transit Data - by
  Civic Tech Toronto
LOCATION:Hybrid
DESCRIPTION:More info:
  https://guild.host/events/civic-meetup-535-headway-usnbxs\n\nHosted by
  Civic Tech Toronto (https://civictech.ca/)\n\nCivic Tech Toronto's weekly
  meetups bring together Torontonians who want to improve the city through
  design\, tech\, and data. This week\, learn about a data-driven framework
  for mitigating bus bunching and gapping using real-time transit data\,
  machine learning\, and optimization models. Followed by project breakout
  sessions.
END:VEVENT
