SUMMARY:Parkdale Day - by Project Parkdale
LOCATION:Parkdale
DESCRIPTION:More info:
  https://www.projectparkdale.com/parkdale-day-2026\n\nHosted by Project
  Parkdale (https://www.projectparkdale.com)\n\nParkdale Day marks the
  anniversary of Parkdale’s annexation to the City of Toronto on March
  23\, 1889. More than a century later\, the day brings together local
  businesses\, artists\, and community members to celebrate the
  neighbourhood as it exists today. Events including 5 markets\, live
  music\, walking tours\, discounts\, food specials\, art shows and more!
END:VEVENT
