LOCATION:Hybrid
DESCRIPTION:More info:
  https://www.torontotenants.org/spring2026tenantschool\n\nHosted by
  Federation of Metro Tenants’ Associations
  (https://www.torontotenants.org)\n\nTenants and Tenant Association
  leaders in Toronto are welcome to come to the Tenant School later\, an
  intensive training with classes taught by lawyers and community
  advocates. Learn about your rights under the law\, meet other tenant
  leaders and strategize to take action against bad landlords!
END:VEVENT
